_:Ncc25f559abcc4ac88ac9ede89f48d1af <http://schema.org/description> "The Forensic Science Regulator ensures that the provision of forensic science services across the criminal justice system is subject to an appropriate regime of scientific quality standards. FSR works with the Home Office ." .
